name: The Treasure Platform

description: A web application that would allow an individual to effectively catalogue family artefacts that they may want to pass down the generations over the years.

name: MISC Website
description: Former (and inaugral) website for the University of Melbourne's Information Security Club.

name: The Adventures of Squidwod
description: A Unity game that involves collecting Eggs from a giant fire-breathing, laser-eyed, grenade-tossing Seagull's nest while dodging its attacks.

name: Landscape Generator
description: A Unity project that dynamically generates a stochastic landscape (terrain + ocean) along with an orbiting sun.

name: Learning to Escape
description: An AI controller that would navigate a car in a map in such a way that it collects the required keys to escape while simultaneously avoiding traps.

name: Luby Jump
description: A flappy-bird-styled mobile game. The 'pipes' in this game are dynamic and so, make the game quite difficult to beat. The current high score (on iOS) sits at 115.
